Paper: hep-th/9712041

Date: 1997-12-04

Title: Summing up the perturbation series in the Schwinger Model

Authors: Tomasz Radozycki

Comments: 10 pages (in REVTEX)

Journal-ref: Eur.Phys.J. C6 (1999) 549-553

Perturbation series for the electron propagator in the Schwinger Model issummed up in a direct way by adding contributions coming from individualFeynman diagrams. The calculation shows the complete agreement betweennonperturbative and perturbative approaches.